name: Jurassic Jungle Rampage
description:
Jurassic Jungle Rampage is a 2d platforming adventure where you play as a hungry dinosaur trying to survive in a very deadly prehistoric jungle filled with traps, monsters and animals. Try to feed your dinosaur and last as long as you can for the high score! How long will you survive?
